profile.name: GreenVision Acquisition Corp.
profile.description: Greenvision Acquisition Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus on target businesses operating in the life sciences and healthcare industries in North America, Europe, and Asia. The company was founded in 2019 and is based in New York, New York.
